9L4r","ref":"Mark.11.3","text":"And if any man say unto you, Why do ye this? say ye that the Lord hath need of him; and straightway he will send him hither.","year":33},{"id":"recO1pqf05Bd6UfAS","ref":"Mark.11.4","text":"And they went their way, and found the colt tied by the door without in a place where two ways met; and they loose him.","year":33},{"id":"recyuDjduiedB7q7u","ref":"Mark.11.5","text":"And certain of them that stood there said unto them, What do ye, loosing the colt?","year":33},{"id":"recbl4q7c0k0XSFMW","ref":"Mark.11.6","text":"And they said unto them even as Jesus had commanded: and they let them go.","year":33},{"id":"rec7yYfhUosvLBlnx","ref":"Mark.11.7","text":"And they brought the colt to Jesus, and cast their garments on him; and he sat upon him.","year":33},{"id":"recc4kFNYqMh9ehke","ref":"Mark.11.8","text":"And many spread their garments in the way: and others cut down branches off the trees, and strawed them in the way.","year":33}]}
